1. On me je *prevario* za novac. (He cheated me out of money.)
2. Ne mogu da verujem da si me *prevario*. (I can't believe you cheated on me.)
3. Svi su mislili da će *prevariti* na ispitu, ali je dobio najvišu ocenu. (Everyone thought he would cheat on the exam, but he got the highest grade.)
4. Njihova firma je bila *prevara*. (Their company was a fraud.)
5. Ne želim da se *prevarim* kao prošli put. (I don't want to be deceived like last time.)
6. Njihov golman je uspeo da *prevari* napadača i sačuva gol. (Their goalkeeper managed to trick the attacker and save the goal.)
7. Često me *prevarila* s obećanjima koja nije ispunila. (She often misled me with promises she didn't keep.)
8. Koliko ljudi je već *prevarilo* taj sajt? (How many people have already been deceived by that website?)
9. Ne možeš me *prevariti* - znam sve tvoje trikove. (You can't deceive me - I know all your tricks.)
10. Nakon što je bio *prevario* u poslu, postao je oprezniji. (After being cheated in business, he became more cautious.)